<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org"
	xmlns:layout="http://www.ultraq.net.nz/thymeleaf/layout"
	layout:decorate="~{fragments/layout}">
<!--    #1. layout 렌더링    -->
<head lang="ko">
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Insert title here</title>
</head>
<body>
	<div layout:fragment="content">
		<h3>OpenAI - ChatGPT</h3>
		<div class="alert alert-primay">일기작성시 일기내용 요약해서 이미지 나타내기.</div>
		<div class="my-3">
			<textarea class="form-control" placeholder="오늘의 일기를 작성해주세요"
				id="userMessage" title="일기작성"></textarea>
		</div>
		<div class="my-3 text-end">
			<input type="button" id="sendBtn" class="btn btn-primary"
				value="일기작성" />
		</div>
		<div id="response" class="alert alert-primary"></div>
		
	<meta name="_csrf" th:content="${_csrf.token}"/>
   <meta name="_csrf_header" th:content="${_csrf.headerName}"/>

	<script>
   $(function(){
    $("#sendBtn").click(function(){
            alert("일기를 작성해주세요!");

   });
   </script>

	</div>


</body>
</html>